---
title: Turkey Meatball Penne made with Pre-Cooked Turkey Meatballs
description: We firmly believe pasta night is a holiday—one that should be celebrated at least once a week, if not more. But when a pasta and meatball craving strikes on a weeknight, who has the time to make those meatballs from scratch? Enter: our not-so-secret ingredient, pre-cooked turkey meatballs. We sear them for a gorgeous crust that forms in just minutes, then toss with al dente penne noodles in a creamy tomato sauce with Parmesan. Now, let the carb celebrations commence!
